SERVER CREATION


BASIC COMMANDS
    
    1)Creating package.json - npm init
    2)Install Express - npm i express
    3)Install JWT - npm i jsonwebtoken
    4)Install cors- npm i cors
BASIC STEPS

    1.Creating a folder
    2.Creating a package.json file
    3.Install express
    4.Creating index.js file
    5.Import express inside the index.js file
    6.Create an app using the express
    7.set up port number
    8.Resolving HTTP Requests
    9.HTTP response code
        1xx - Information
        2xx - Success
        3xx - Redirection
        4xx - Client Error
        5xx - Server Error
    
    10. JWT (JSON web token)token - For authentication
    sign()

    11. Middleware
        1. Application specific middleware - for entire application
        2. Router specific middleware - token vaidation- verify()

    12. Database Integration
        Install mongoose
        db connect via mongoose
        create model using mongoose
    
    13. Asynchronous function Resolving
        Resolve - .then()
        Reject - catch()
    14. CORS -
        Install cors
    
